      "acceptanceCriteria": "Basic documentation of simulation setup and analyst qualifications sufficient at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal use error assessment is not required. The simulation was performed by a qualified CFD analyst with documented training in ANSYS Fluent and rotating machinery applications. Setup was reviewed by a second analyst."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
