      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form selection (turbulence model, hemolysis power-law model) must be documented with basic justification.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required. The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on published literature for rotating blood-contacting devices. Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model was applied consistently with prior FDA benchmark studies."
    },
    {
