      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal sensitivity analysis of model inputs is not required. Fluid properties (density 1056 kg/m3, viscosity 0.0035 Pa·s for blood analog) are documented and traceable to the FDA benchmark dataset. Boundary conditions are specified from experimental measurements."
    },
