      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples used for validation must be documented with sufficient characterization to confirm representativeness.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, detailed test sample characterization beyond basic documentation is not required. The FDA generic centrifugal pump used for experimental validation is a standardized benchmark geometry with published dimensional tolerances, providing adequate representativeness for this risk level."
    },
