    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriate to scope at MRL 2 given the medium model influence and documented analyst qualifications. CFD predictions of relative hemolysis index agree with experimental data within 15% across all five operating conditions, and all predicted RH values satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
